<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/style.css" />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/8dabcbb496.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script defer src="scripts/script.js"></script>
    <title>Kathy May Music</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section id="hero">
      <nav id="desktop-nav">
        <a href="#contact">
            <img
            src="./assets/Fiverr Premium Kit/SVG Vector Files/Transparent Logo.svg"
            alt="Kath May Music logo"
          />
        </a>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#music">Music</a></li>
          <li><a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <nav id="mobile-nav"></nav>
      <div class="hamburger">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-container">
          <nav>
              <ul>
                  <li>
                      <a href="#about">About</a>
                  </li>
                   <li>
                      <a href="#music">Music</a>
                  </li>
                   <li>
                      <a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a>
                  </li>
                   <li>
                      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
                  </li>
              </ul>
          </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="main-content">
        <div class="intro">
          <p class="eyebrow">Nelson, New Zealand</p>
          <h1>Kath May <span class="text-gradient">Music</span></h1>
          <h2>Singer & Pianist</h2>
          <h3>Weddings | Functions | Corporate Events</h3>
          <p>
            Get ready to be enchanted by Kath May, Nelson's own Fleetwood Mac songstress! With captivating vocals and a passion for the classics, Kath brings the timeless magic of Stevie Nicks and Co. to life in intimate performances that will leave you spellbound and yearning for more.
          </p>
          <div class="player">
            <audio class="audio" src=""></audio>
            <button class="backward-btn">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-backward"></i>
            </button>
            <button class="play-btn">
              <i id="playIcon" class="fa-solid fa-play"></i>
            </button>
            <button class="forward-btn">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-forward"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="progress-container">
            <div class="progress-bar"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="song-titles">
            <h3></h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            This exclusive collection features Kath's captivating renditions of Stevie Nicks' most beloved songs, carefully crafted to transport you to a world of dreams, love, and mystique. Press play and let the enchantment begin.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="img-container">
          <img src="./assets/singer-fgirl.png" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
     <div class="background">
        <div class="biography">
            <div class="img">
                <img src="assets/singer_02.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="blurb">
                <h2>Biography</h2>
                <h3>Echoes of Fleetwood Mac, Soul of Kath May</h3>
                <p>
                    Nelson-based singer-songwriter Kath May has always been under the spell of Fleetwood Mac's timeless harmonies and poetic lyrics. With a voice that echoes the haunting beauty of Stevie Nicks, Kath weaves her own magic into the band's beloved classics.
                    A lifelong musician, Kath cut her teeth on the Nelson music scene, performing in various bands and collaborations before discovering her true calling as a Fleetwood Mac interpreter. Her mesmerizing live shows have captivated audiences across the South Island, transporting them to a world of dreams, love, and mystique.
                    With a setlist that spans Fleetwood Mac's iconic discography, from "Rhiannon" to "Landslide", Kath May's performances are a must-experience for fans of the legendary band. Join her on a journey through the music that has inspired generations – and let the enchantment begin.</p>
                    <h3>Timeless Songs, Unforgettable Moments</h3>
                    <p>
                    As a singer and pianist, Kath brings more than just a tribute act to the stage – she brings a whole evening's atmosphere. From soft, acoustic piano sets during a wedding ceremony to a full-voiced, band-backed performance at a corporate gala, every setlist is shaped around the occasion and the crowd in the room.
                    Couples and event planners across Nelson and the wider South Island return to Kath again and again for her warmth, professionalism, and ability to read a room – turning a simple background soundtrack into a night people still talk about long after the last song ends.</p>
                    <h4><a style="color:#ffcba0" href="#contact">Join the Enchantment: Book Kath May for Your Next Event</a></h4>
            </div>
        </div>
     </div>
    </section>
    <section id="music">
        <div class="gig-container">
            <p class="eyebrow">What's On</p>
            <h3>Events and <span>Shows</span></h3>
            <div class="gig-info">     
                <% if(events.length === 0) { %>
                    <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/01.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/02.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/03.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                <% } else if(events.length === 1) { %>
                    <div class="info info-1">
                        <span>$<%= events[0].eventPrice %></span>
                        <img src="assets/01.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2><%= events[0].eventName %></h2>
                          <small><%= events[0].eventDate %> / <%= events[0].eventTime %> / <%= events[0].eventVenue %></small>
                          <p><%= events[0].eventDescription %></p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/02.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/03.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                 <% } else if(events.length === 2) { %>
                    <div class="info info-1">
                        <span>$<%= events[0].eventPrice %></span>
                        <img src="assets/01.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2><%= events[0].eventName %></h2>
                          <small><%= events[0].eventDate %> / <%= events[0].eventTime %> / <%= events[0].eventVenue %></small>
                          <p><%= events[0].eventDescription %></p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span>$<%= events[1].eventPrice %></span>
                        <img src="assets/02.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2><%= events[1].eventName %></h2>
                          <small><%= events[1].eventDate %> / <%= events[1].eventTime %> / <%= events[1].eventVenue %></small>
                          <p><%= events[1].eventDescription %></p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info info-1">
                        <span></span>
                        <img src="assets/03.jpg" alt="">
                        <div class="details">
                          <h2>Coming Soon!</h2>
                          <small>TBD</small>
                          <p>Details Coming Soon!</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                <% }else { %>
                    <% let imgCounter = 1 %>
                    <% events.forEach(event => { %>
                        <div class="info info-1">
                            <span>$<%= event.eventPrice %></span>
                            <img src="assets/0<%= imgCounter %>.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="details">
                              <h2><%= event.eventName %></h2>
                              <small><%= event.eventDate %> / <%= event.eventTime %> / <%= event.eventVenue %></small>
                              <p><%= event.eventDescription %></p>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <% imgCounter++ %>
                    <% }) %>
                <% } %>
                </div>   
            </div>
  
     
     
    </section>
    <section id="testimonials">
        <div class="slider">
            <div class="slide active">
                Kath is a true vocal powerhouse!" - David K.
            </div>
            <div class="slide">
                Kath has a voice that can move mountains! - Rachel G
            </div>
            <div class="slide">
                Kath's voice is pure magic! - Emily R
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script>
        const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');
        let index = 0;

        function changeSlide() {
            slides[index].classList.remove('active');
            index = (index + 1) % slides.length;
            slides[index].classList.add('active');
        }
        slides[0].classList.add('active');
        setInterval(changeSlide, 4000); 
    </script>
    <section id="contact">
        <div class="form-container">
            <div>
                <h2>Contact Me</h2>
                <small>All enquiries use the contact form below</small>
            </div>
            <div class="contact">
                <form id="contactForm" action="https://formsubmit.co/kia-kaha@hotmail.co.nz" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="/thankyou.html">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New submission!">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="name">Name:</label>
                      <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="email">Email:</label>
                      <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="message">Message:</label>
                      <textarea id="message" name="message"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <input type="submit" value="Send">
                  
                  </form>
                  <div class="contact-info">
                    <h2>Kath May | Singer </h2>
                    <div>021 615 593</div>
                    <div>kathmaymusic@gmail.com</div>
                    <div>123 main street <br>Nelson <br>tel: 04 1234567</div>
                    <img class="contact-logo" src="assets/Fiverr Premium Kit/SVG Vector Files/Transparent Logo.svg" alt="Kath May Music logo">
                  </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="site-footer">Kath May &copy; All Rights Reserved 2025</footer>
  </body>
</html>

